name: sales-team
version: 1.0.0
title: 🏢 Sales Team — Multi-Agent Sales System
description: v1.0.0 | Complete multi-agent sales system with lead scraping, verification, outreach drafting, and deal closing orchestration.
instructions: |
  # Sales Team — Multi-Agent Sales System

  ## Overview
  The Sales Team MAS automates the B2B sales pipeline with 5 specialized agents working together:

  1. **🎯 Sales Orchestrator** — Main coordinator, decomposes queries and dispatches work
  2. **🔍 Lead Scraper** — Finds B2B leads matching ICP via web search
  3. **✅ Lead Verifier** — MANDATORY quality gate, verifies and scores leads
  4. **✉️ Outreach Drafter** — Creates personalized outreach messages
  5. **🤝 Deal Closer** — Develops follow-up cadence and objection handling

  ## Pipeline Flow
  ```
  User Query → Sales Orchestrator
                  ↓
              Lead Scraper
                  ↓
          ╔═ Lead Verifier ═╗  ← MANDATORY QUALITY GATE
          ║ (filters spam,   ║
          ║  cross-checks,   ║
          ║  scores 0-1)     ║
          ╚══════════════════╝
                  ↓
           Outreach Drafter
                  ↓
             Deal Closer
                  ↓
        Final Recommendation + Sources
  ```

  ## Critical Rules
  - **Quality Gate**: ALL leads MUST pass through lead-verifier before outreach-drafter
  - **Source Transparency**: Every recommendation includes source URLs
  - **Confidence Scoring**: Every lead has a confidence score (0-1)
  - **No Fabrication**: Never make up leads or company information

  ## Usage
  ```bash
  goose run --recipe /tmp/sales-team/recipe/sales-team.yaml
  ```

  ### Example queries:
  - "Find AI startups in San Francisco for our enterprise SaaS"
  - "Verify these 3 leads and draft outreach for verified ones"
  - "Help me close a deal with Acme Corp in logistics AI"
  - "Review our sales pipeline for Q3"
